{"tid":2422402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女廚師觀塘堵路現場管有雷射筆 判入獄兩個月","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T15:29:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"59d308e99e3654ca3e212d7889188ba8f5c13121","tid":2422402,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"網民前年10月發起十八區再開花的「神獸罷鷲」行動，繼續爭取五大訴求，同時反對蒙面惡法與反警暴。當日觀塘區亦出現堵路，警方接報到場掃蕩時，在現場附近發現一名女廚師與約10名黑衣人逃走。女廚師遭截獲，並在其背囊內搜出雷射筆。她今在觀塘裁判法院承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，裁判官稱判監無可避免，判她入獄兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告來自單親家庭，任職廚師，惟因受疫情影響，現僅能兼職工作。事發距今約16個月，被告精神飽受影響。她明知會被判監，仍選擇認罪，望能輕判，承諾不會再犯。辯方又呈上被告父親及好友撰寫的求情信，兩人均讚賞被告為人。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官徐綺薇判刑時強調，上訴庭已提及同類案件的嚴重性以及雷射筆對人眼的傷害。雖然被告原本沒有案底，且選擇認罪，但判監仍是無可避免，判被告入獄兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/ZA2UPFZZMBGQDLWQLTJQOHEPTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FZA2UPFZZMBGQDLWQLTJQOHEPTQ%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=8006f1f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FZA2UPFZZMBGQDLWQLTJQOHEPTQ%2F&h=3a0af8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/ZA2UPFZZMBGQDLWQLTJQOHEPTQ/</a>"},{"pid":"1a84c0673b46f8560b59243524e94e80a11403c3","tid":2422402,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\